<button aria-label="Translate to Persian">
  <svg>...</svg>
</button>

<!-- Live Regions for Status Updates -->
<div aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
  Translation in progress...
</div>
```

### Keyboard Navigation
```css
/* Focus indicators */
*:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--primary);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Skip links */
.skip-link {
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  left: 6px;
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  padding: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  z-index: 1000;
}

.skip-link:focus {
  top: 6px;
}
```

### High Contrast Mode
```css
@media (prefers-contrast: high) {
  .card {
    border: 2px solid;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    border: 2px solid white;
  }
}
```

## Animation and Transitions

### Micro-interactions
```css
/* Button press feedback */
.btn:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

/* Loading spinner */
.spinner {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  border: 2px solid #f3f4f6;
  border-top: 2px solid var(--primary);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
  0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
```

### Page Transitions
```css
/* Smooth transitions between states */
.translation-box {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  animation: slideIn 0.3s ease forwards;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}
```

## Persian Text Handling

### RTL Layout
```css
/* Persian text container */
.persian-text {
  direction: rtl;
  text-align: right;
  font-family: "Noto Naskh Arabic", "Vazirmatn", Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
}

/* Mixed content */
.mixed-content {
  direction: ltr;
  text-align: left;
}

.mixed-content .persian {
  direction: rtl;
  display: inline-block;
}
```

### Font Loading
```css
